ikaaro 0.62.8 (2011/11/02)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Changes
-------

New features:

- Now a progress bar is shown when uploading a file (#573)

- Add an editor for CSS files (#1033)
  http://www.cdolivet.com/editarea/

- There are two new configuration options: max-width and max-height.
  When set, uploaded images will be scaled down (if needed), to save
  space in the database.

Many minor issues have been resolved, including #1223, #1229 and #1235.


